As we might expect, neighborhood is a significant predictor of income. Controlling for neighborhood and source, other significant predictors to note: Request for new street light significantly predicts income at the 5% level with a coefficient of almost $70k. Request for service from the port authority significantly predicts income at the 10% level with a coefficient of $51k. Request type other with detail significantly predicts income at the 5% level with a coefficient of $74k. Customer callback for traffic engineering is negatively and significantly correlated with income. *Complaints to the entertainment commission are negatively and significantly correlated with income.
